# Security Rules

- Authenticate protected routes; authorize at use-case boundary (not UI-only)
- Least privilege roles: Customer, Commerce Admin, Content Admin, Writer, SEO Editor, Medical Reviewer, Creator, Brand, Finance, Support, Super Admin
- Prevent IDOR — verify ownership on sensitive reads/writes
- Validate all external input with Zod/DTOs
- Never log tokens, passwords, OTPs, PAN/CVV
- Never store raw card data — provider tokens only
- Secrets only in env/secret manager — never commit `.env`
- Rate-limit auth and sensitive POSTs
- Audit privileged admin/finance/publish/award actions
- Private media via signed URLs
